lazysite is a self-contained Perl CGI application and bundles no third-party
source. Its runtime dependencies are Perl core modules plus the optional
Template Toolkit, Archive::Zip and DB_File - each under its own copyright and
licence, enumerated with SPDX identifiers in dist/config/sbom-deps.json and in
the generated CycloneDX SBOM shipped with each release.
